{"tid":2220884,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港民研料今日可完成問卷收集 ....","createTime":"2020-09-28T03:39:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-28T03:39:56.000Z","uid":29244,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5d464d4ef7f2c70654ede7a6994e8b5c33e65cee","tid":2220884,"uid":29244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T03:39:56.000Z","msg":"香港民意研究所於本周一（21日）開始進行民主黨委託的民調，決定民主派立法會議員去留。香港民研主席兼行政總裁鍾庭耀表示，調查工作相當順利，預計最快今日（25日）可完成所有問卷收集，會在下周一（28日）完成報告，民主黨應在下周二（29日）早上11時半公布結果。他說，受訪市民算是合作，相信出現不可靠或弄虛作假的回應不會太多，亦會驗證數據準確度。<br />\n<br />\n香港民研每年都會就市民對施政報告期望進行調查，惟鍾庭耀稱今年因資源有限決定取消，施政報告即日民調則會繼續。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200925/s00001/1601024601356/%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%B0%91%E7%A0%94%E6%96%99%E4%BB%8A%E6%97%A5%E5%8F%AF%E5%AE%8C%E6%88%90%E5%95%8F%E5%8D%B7%E6%94%B6%E9%9B%86-9-29%E5%85%AC%E5%B8%83%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%B4%BE%E5%8E%BB%E7%95%99%E6%B0%91%E8%AA%BF%E7%B5%90%E6%9E%9C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200925%2Fs00001%2F1601024601356%2F%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2583-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%25A0%2594%25E6%2596%2599%25E4%25BB%258A%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%258F%25AF%25E5%25AE%258C%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2595%258F%25E5%258D%25B7%25E6%2594%25B6%25E9%259B%2586-9-29%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25B8%2583%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E5%258E%25BB%25E7%2595%2599%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E7%25B5%2590%25E6%259E%259C&d=4SaXJ4tauImRU00LhBBHUkuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=1841b15a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200925%2Fs00001%2F1601024601356%2F%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2583-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%25A0%2594%25E6%2596%2599%25E4%25BB%258A%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%258F%25AF%25E5%25AE%258C%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2595%2